### Description

Currently scheme `https://example.org/{locale}/{app-routing}` is hardcoded in [AngularAppEngine](https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/blob/d6b3074812676142559fe396d345401c15296c02/packages/angular/ssr/src/app-engine.ts#L72)

Scheme `https://{locale}.example.org/{app-routing}` may be implemented with client side rendering and web-server virtualhosts only but not with SSR.

### Describe the solution you'd like

Some kind of AngularServerAppHandlerInterface, DefaultServerAppHandler implementation and a way to provide your own 

also move [`redirectBasedOnAcceptLanguage` logic](https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/blob/d6b3074812676142559fe396d345401c15296c02/packages/angular/ssr/src/app-engine.ts#L78) inside 

```typescript
export interface AngularServerAppHandlerInterface {
  handle(request: Request, requestContext?: unknown): Promise<null | Response>; // resolve app, handle request and redirects inside
}

class DefaultServerAppHandler implements AngularServerAppHandlerInterface {
  async handle(request: Request, requestContext?: unknown): Promise<null | Response> {
    const serverApp = await this.getAngularServerAppForRequest(request);

    if (serverApp) {
      return serverApp.handle(request, requestContext);
    }

    if (this.supportedLocales.length > 1) {
      // Redirect to the preferred language if i18n is enabled.
      return this.redirectBasedOnAcceptLanguage(request);
    }

    return null;
  }

  private async getAngularServerAppForRequest(request: Request): Promise<AngularServerApp | null> {
    ...

    return serverApp;
  }

  private redirectBasedOnAcceptLanguage(request: Request): null | Response {
    ...

    return null;
  }
}
```

### Describe alternatives you've considered

As alternative i've tried to fork AngularAppEngine and setup my own implementation of i18n-routing but it's imposible because of [hardcoded to @angular/ssr manifest singleton](https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/blob/d6b3074812676142559fe396d345401c15296c02/packages/angular/build/src/tools/esbuild/application-code-bundle.ts#L455).
